Add ArcGIS Map 18

1.   Select  ArcGIS Map from visualization pane

2.   Drag and drop “State” from STD Cases table in the location field

3.   Drag and drop “AvgCases” To Size Field

4.   Drag and drop “YoY” To Color Field


1.   From  ArcGIS Map Expand the Map tools

2.   Click the Layer list

3.   Open the symbology from the three dots and choose the color pane as shows

1.   From the format Pane open the Map tools

2.   Turn on the zoom tools

3.   Increase size of the map till it fits well

2. Select Image from Insert

3. Upload already saved screenshot from folder

5. Select Text box and wright "Low" and put both on opposite side of the pane
